We use subtasks extensively.  We just had an problem solved for us by Keith that resulted from a subtask that had no parent.  We ran the integrity checker but it didn't find this problem.  It would be great to have the parent-subtask relationship checked by the integrity checker so we can address issues like this ourselves.

